<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">This is so tough! They are a little bit similar but so entirely different! In my opinion, I liked Speak better than Perks just because it resonated wi<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">This is so tough! They are a little bit similar but so entirely different! In my opinion, I liked Speak better than Perks just because it resonated with me more. I felt a deeper connection and it touched me more emotionally. So I'd go with Speak, but they are both beautiful books.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
